Kill condition: if apparent success depends on omitted forced modes, threshold
retuning, or post hoc rephasing, reject it as non-presentable.

### Step 4 - Interpret Outcomes With Symmetric Standards

Depends on: Step 3.

Action: if
`F_SS(1/12)`
